        "text_7kwRFb": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>All of our skincare is built around five skin types and we want to help you work out which one is yours. It takes a couple of minutes and a little personal observation. No special lighting or magnifying mirror, just a sense of what your skin actually does over an ordinary day.<br/><br/>One thing to say first. Your skin might not be the same all over. Plenty of people are one type on the face and another on the hands, and that's normal. There's a short note at the end on how to handle it. For now, picture the skin you most want to look after, then answer these two simple questions about it.<br/></p>",
            "width": "fit-content",
